# Build Plan — module `{{MODULE_NAME}}`

> Decomposes the design spec into **bounded, single-module build tickets**. Each ticket is small
> enough for one agent in one worktree, lists the EXACT files it touches, the schemas/endpoints it
> adds, the **ACs it turns green**, and the **gate commands** that prove it. The orchestrator spawns
> tickets per the run-plan; it re-runs the gates itself and never trusts a self-declared "done."

- **Spec:** `{{DESIGN_SPEC_PATH}}` · **ACs:** `AC-{{AREA}}-{{AC_RANGE}}`
- **Ticket families:** `B-{{AREA}}-N` (backend) · `F-{{AREA}}-N` (frontend)
- Tickets are filed as `<id>-<slug>.todo.md` (see `ticket.todo.md.tmpl`) into
  `.orchestrator/tasks/inbox/`.

